/*
make sure to divide your html page properly using <div> tags with appropriate ids and classes
lets call all of the things to be styled as elements
elements could be built in tags like a, h1, p ... or things such as divs with assigned ids and classes
*/

tag {
variable1: value1;
variable2: value2;
}

#id {
}

.class{

}

means element1 and element2 have same rules
element1 , element2 {
variable1: value1;
variable2: value2;
}


means element2 IN element1 has the below rules
element1  element2 {
variable1: value1;
variable2: value2;
}
